{
  "stem": "17625.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- but this was already-- this was already end of-- end of April, May and I was liberated in January, January 19, exactly two years to the day, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Two years to the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if I would go further, plenty of people died by the march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- in-- but Sonderkommando, there was still a danger wherever they come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so So that they didn't want us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had no-- no way of-- of-- of helping this here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] should I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People are stronger than anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You adjust to any situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you know that the end of the road comes, you live this way, then-- then you have a way of living it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can tell you an example.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was transport from Greeks, Greeks, you know, small people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they were-- you know what their job was?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their job was stomping-- stomping the ashes, stomping the ashes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And stomping the ashes was a-- was a dirty job because it was hot, hot ashes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you had to-- you had to-- you had to take them out when they're hot, stomp them when they're hot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and-- it burns all around you, the smell, you know, for the lungs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were working and singing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They knew what what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They knew their end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were singing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they make-- they made also like-- like a little show.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They made a show about this-- I told you in the papers there was one [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We called him the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was always coming when there was a transport, you know, to bring the good news.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So this guy, this Greek, he-- he-- he simulated him.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
